      "text": [
        " «لاَ وَ لَكِنْ يُطَافُ بِهِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2821 - Ishaq ibn Ammar asked Imam Abu Ibrahim (as) about a severely ill person who is unable to perform circumambulation around the Kaaba.\nThe Imam (as) replied: \"No, but he should be carried and circumambulated with.\""
        ]
